WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.143 --> 00:00:05.136
''I shall wait for you. . . ''

00:00:05.663 --> 00:00:13.138
''I shall wait for you
till the end of Time''

00:00:14.223 --> 00:00:18.136
''May God bring about
such a day. . . ''

00:00:19.063 --> 00:00:22.135
''that heralds your arrival''

00:00:30.863 --> 00:00:34.651
''I shall wait for you''

00:00:43.663 --> 00:00:51.138
''You are the one
my dejected eyes look for''

00:00:52.143 --> 00:00:59.140
''I wander in the quest
of meeting you''

00:01:00.663 --> 00:01:05.134
''May I carry on with the
same passion and obsession. . . ''

00:01:11.663 --> 00:01:14.655
''for you to arrive''

00:01:15.463 --> 00:01:19.138
''May God bring Time
to an end. . . ''

00:01:19.663 --> 00:01:22.655
''to herald your arrival''

00:01:23.663 --> 00:01:26.655
''I shall wait for you''

00:01:36.463 --> 00:01:44.143
''I shall lay my life
at your feet''

00:01:44.663 --> 00:01:52.138
''I shall entrust to you
what is rightfully yours''

00:01:59.663 --> 00:02:03.656
''Just when I'm about to leave. . . ''

00:02:04.143 --> 00:02:07.135
''I wish you could arrive''

00:02:08.143 --> 00:02:12.136
''May God bring Time
to an end. . . ''

00:02:12.663 --> 00:02:16.133
''to bring about your arrival''

